dct_title_s: Map of Arundel County showwing geological formations
dct_description_sm: Maryland Geological Survey. County Maps. Anne Arundel Sheet Maryland Geological Survey. County Reports v.7 Anne Arundel United States. Geological Survey Companion text: Anne Arundel County / Homer P. Little; J. C. Britton; C. R. Zappone, Jr; O. L. Fassig; B. D. Wood; L. A. Bauer; F. W. Besley. Maryland Geological Survey. County Reports v.7 Anne Arundel County. 1917. 232p. 4 maps in separete atlas. Relief shown by 20 feet contour interval. Stratigraphic column, cross section. Another copy of map with source publication.
